<h1>Welcome to the Signup Page</h1>
<p>We are glad that you are becoming a member today.  Once you fill out this form below, an email will be sent to the email address you provided.  Click the activation link in the email, and you are all set.</p><p>Membership allows you to post in the Forum, create your own blog, submit Comments and Product Reviews, Add photos, Create friendships and so much more.</p><p>You will have fun, and we are glad you chose <%= $SITE_NAME %>.</p>

<%= error_messages_for :user %>
<% form_for :user, :url => users_path do |f| -%>
<p><label for="login">Login</label><br/>
<%= f.text_field :login %></p>

<p><label for="email">Email</label><br/>
<%= f.text_field :email %></p>

<p><label for="password">Password</label><br/>
<%= f.password_field :password %></p>

<p><label for="password_confirmation">Confirm Password</label><br/>
<%= f.password_field :password_confirmation %></p>
<p><label for="terms">Terms of Service</label><br />
	<%= f.check_box :terms_of_service %>  I agree to the <%= link_to "Terms of Service", {:controller => 'site', :action => 'terms'}, :popup => true %></p>

<p><%= submit_tag 'Sign up' %></p>
<% end -%>
